                <note rend="inline" type="source">393.115/11–1549: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul General at Shanghai</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">McConaughy</hi>
                    </persName>)<note n="8" xml:id="d1159fn8">Repeated to the Chargé in China as
                        telCan No. 757, November 16, 4 p. m.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-11-15T19:00:00-05:00"
                            >November 15, 1949—7 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>2271. Urtel unnumbered, November 15. Pls endeavor most urgently obtain full
                    report all details regarding Natl gunboat’s attack <hi rend="italic">Flying
                        Cloud</hi>. Particularly desire info re fol: Did Natl gunboat signal <hi
                        rend="italic">Cloud</hi> and at what position; did gunboat fire warning
                    shot; at what point did gunboat open fire which inflicted damage <hi
                        rend="italic">Cloud</hi>.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
